text: Vojislav Gološin (born 27 February 1930) is a Serbian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Serbian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Yugoslavia Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zrenjanin
